Here&#39;s a corrected, annotated version:
```c
#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;string.h&gt;

int main() {
    int e;
    char name[100] = &quot;&quot;; // Allow for up to 100 characters
    printf(&quot;Enter a name : \n&quot;);
